Text: Sweet, I didn't realize they had a What If series so recently.

Wow, this is a giant middle-finger to everyone that was upset, and still is, with One More Day. I thought it was going to be more like What If? Peter gave the killing blow against the Kingpin and MJ & Peter decided to let May go peacefully...instead of you know that other business. They ignored the much better What If? story to say "Hey, guess what? Deal still stands even in an alternate reality!"
